abstract.text: A type for an event that indicates the creation of a file.

inlineContent.text: If the file doesn’t exist — either because it’s awaiting authorization or a client denied authorization —  this type contains the parent directory and file name of the proposed file. If the file does exist, as is the case with notifications of successful file creation, this type contains the full path of the created file. Use the
